'''Arpadüzü''' ({{lang-hy|italic=yes|Պերետես, Peretes}}) (also, '''Kolkhizashen''', '''Kolkhozashen''', '''Kolxozaşen''', and '''Mashadishen''') is a village in the [[Martuni Province]] of the de facto [[Republic of Artsakh]], de jure part of the Republic of Azerbaijan.

