'''Gornji Breg''' (Горњи Брег) is a small geographical region in [[Serbia]]. It is located in north-eastern [[Bačka]], in the [[Vojvodina]] province. There is also a village named [[Gornji Breg, Senta|Gornji Breg]], which is situated in this region.

