===GAA county colours=== [[GAA county colours]] are used to represent [[Counties of Ireland|Irish counties]] in the [[Gaelic Athletic Association]]'s inter-county competitions, most notably the [[All-Ireland Senior Football Championship]] in [[Gaelic football]] and the [[All-Ireland Senior Hurling Championship]] in [[Hurling]].
